FeeNames DataTable and CRUD architecture

- Align FeeNamesController with GradeController: server-side DataTable in index, AJAX create/edit/delete, show and edit JSON endpoints.
- Use StoreFeeNames request for validation like StoreGrades.
- Load classes via AJAX for add/edit modal and render class-specific amount/remarks rows.
- Implement top-level type behavior: monthly / yearly / custom with month selectors.
- Use FeeNames model hasMany Fees, Fee belongsTo FeeNames + Classroom + Grade.
- Ensure data is saved in transactions and related Fee records are synced on update.
- Keep UI DataTable structure same as Grades.blade.php.
